https://lschema.org/description.@value: The time or time-period the observed values are related to. When the subject of the report is a patient, this is usually either the time of the procedure or of specimen collection(s), but very often the source of the date/time is not known, only the date/time itself.
String of characters used to identify a name or a resource
An instant in time - known at least to the second
A string which has at least one character and no leading or trailing whitespace and where there is no whitespace other than single spaces in the contents
The status of the diagnostic report.
